HSA and eMERLIN, as well as the Chandra X-ray data
point reported in Palliyaguru et al. (2019), are added
to the fit. These fits also assume equipartition of en-
ergy between particles and magnetic fields such that
�e = �B = 0.33. We set the electron energy index,
p = 2.5, which is typical for GRB afterglows, as expected
